---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GitHub from "../assets/github.svg";
import LinkedIn from "../assets/linkedin.svg";
---

<Layout
  title="Keziah Rackley-Gale | Frontend Developer | React + TypeScript"
  description="Passionate software developer with a track record of driving impactful projects from conception to successful execution. Led the development and global release of a top-ranked mobile application in New Zealand. Expert in frontend technologies including React, React Native, and TypeScript. Skilled in streamlining processes, fostering collaboration, and creating exceptional user experiences. 👩‍💻✨"
>
  <header>
    <h1>Keziah Rackley-Gale</h1>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/keziahrg"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            aria-label="GitHub"
          >
            <GitHub width="1em" width="1em" font-size="1.375rem" />
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/keziahrg/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            aria-label="LinkedIn"
          >
            <LinkedIn width="1em" width="1em" font-size="1.375rem" />
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    <h2>Frontend Developer Building Awesome User Experiences</h2>
    <p>
      Kia ora! I'm Keziah — a frontend developer with a passion for crafting
      sleek, user-focused experiences using React, React Native, and TypeScript.
    </p>
    <p>
      After starting my career in Aotearoa New Zealand, I've spent the last two
      years working remotely in London.
    </p>
    <p>
      Over the past five years, I've honed my skills at a top-tier marketing
      agency and a boutique digital studio, bringing creative ideas to life with
      clean, functional code.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now, I'm ready to take on my next adventure — <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/keziahrg/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        aria-label="LinkedIn">let's chat</a
      > about what we can build together.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
